OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA largely cloudy start with
OL,6,Fsome patchy light drizzle around, but
OL,7,Fbright along the west coast. Gradually
OL,8,Fbrightening up in the afternoon with
OL,9,Fthe best of the sunshine across
OL,10,FArgyll. Feeling warm.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FA bright end to the day then
OL,13,Fremaining dry overnight with long
OL,14,Fclear spells. Some patchy low cloud
OL,15,Fwill feed in from the east.
OL,16,
OL,17,CMonday:FAny early low cloud will
OL,18,Fquickly clear then a dry day with
OL,19,Fplenty of warm sunshine. Becoming very
OL,20,Fwarm in the afternoon.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
